<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/custom.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/pages-style/deskripsi.css">
</head>
<body class="bg">
    <div class="container-fluid p-0 d-flex h-100">

        <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
        
        <div class="flex-fill">
            <div class="p-2 d-xl-none d-flex text-white bg-primary">
                <a href="#" class="text-white" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#bdSidebar">
                    <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
                </a>
                <span class="ms-3">GetaMeal</span>
            </div>

            <!-- anything  -->
            <div class="container mt-4 mb-4" style="width: 80%;">
                <form action="" class="input-group">
                    <input type="text" class="search-left form-control search-bar" id="" placeholder="Cari kuliner">
                    <button type="submit" class="search-right input-group-text"><i class="fa fa-search" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <!-- main panel -->
            <div class="main-panel">
                <div class="main">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <div class="title d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                            <h2 class="" style="font-weight: bold;">PROSEDUR MAKANAN</h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grey-area p-4 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="left-desc container col-lg-6">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-12">
                                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-link">
                                            <div class="row gutter-none" style="border-bottom: 1px solid black;">
                                                <img class="AddIcon px-0 col-2 text-black" src="/src/icon/plus_add.svg">
                                                <span class="AddBook px-0 col-10 text-black" style="font-weight: bold;">Add To Bookmark</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
                                        <img class="img card-img-top" src="https://www.masakapahariini.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Resep-Sayur-Lodeh-Simple-Kuah-Santan-780x440.jpg" alt="">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-12">
                                        <div class="row mt-5 d-flex justify-content-between">
                                            <div class="col-4">
                                                <button onclick="redirectToInfo()" type="button" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-weight: bold;  width: 100%; border-radius: 10px;">Kembali</button>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-4">
                                                <!-- <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-weight: bold;  width: 100%; border-radius: 10px;">Prosedur</button> -->
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-4">
                                                <button onclick="redirectResep()" type="button" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-weight: bold; width: 100%; border-radius: 10px;">Resep</button>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="right-desc col-lg-6">
                                
                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                                    <div class="title-food d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                                        <h3 class="" style="font-weight: bold; margin: 5px 0;">PECEL MADIUN</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="mx-4 row">
                                    <div class="col"6>
                                        <h5>Cara Membuat</h5>
                                        <ol style="font-size: 14px;">
                                            <li>Rebus ceker hingga mendidih, kecilkan api.</li>
                                            <li>Masukkan daun salam, lengkuas, dan bumbu halus, dan gula merah, aduk. Masukkan labu siam, aduk rata. Masak hingga setengah matang.</li>
                                            <li>Tambahkan terung dan santan, aduk rata.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col" style="border-left: 1px solid black;">
                                        <ol style="font-size: 14px;" start="4"> 
                                            <li>Masukkan kacang panjang, cabai hijau, dan Royco Kaldu Ayam, masak sambil diaduk supaya santan tidak pecah.</li>
                                            <li>Saat semua bahan sayuran sudah matang, masukkan daun melinjo, aduk hingga layu. Angkat dan sajikan.</li>
                                        </ol>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-IQsoLXl5PILFhosVNubq5LC7Qb9DXgDA9i+tQ8Zj3iwWAwPtgFTxbJ8NT4GN1R8p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/script/food.js"></script>
    <script src="/script/dashboard.js"></script>
</body>
</html>